所以呢個都係中共高明之處<br />\n從來需要高調表忠既只有外人（港企）<br />\n而央企根本唔需要表忠，自然可以靜雞雞做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5beb45137e370c001771231a6379884ce41426a6","tid":1627923,"uid":11447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T19:08:51.000Z","msg":"要搵sasac名冊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1335e4e4b95ed82c96c380884996ce6460358e7","tid":1627923,"uid":284304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T19:10:12.000Z","msg":"香港有邊D央企"},{"pid":"b403459bc6ac6611981339d80ccaa010fde6f4ef","tid":1627923,"uid":269125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1335e4e4b95ed82c96c380884996ce6460358e7","tid":1627923,"uid":284304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T19:10:12.000Z","msg":"香港有邊D央企"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T19:12:58.000Z","msg":"中銀香港<br />\n中信泰富<br />\n中國人壽<br />\n太平保險<br />\n中國移動<br />\n興業證券"},{"pid":"5c188adf980f295e2372624eb93f23981f5c2b23","tid":1627923,"uid":31151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b403459bc6ac6611981339d80ccaa010fde6f4ef","tid":1627923,"uid":269125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1335e4e4b95ed82c96c380884996ce6460358e7","tid":1627923,"uid":284304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T19:10:12.000Z","msg":"香港有邊D央企"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T19:12:58.000Z","msg":"中銀香港<br />\n中信泰富<br />\n中國人壽<br />\n太平保險<br />\n中國移動<br />\n興業證券"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T19:14:23.000Z","msg":"咪又係呢堆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e21147a58bce1ad9e6c13681d8ff895cfd383f5","tid":1627923,"uid":269125,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5c188adf980f295e2372624eb93f23981f5c2b23","tid":1627923,"uid":31151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b403459bc6ac6611981339d80ccaa010fde6f4ef","tid":1627923,"uid":269125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1335e4e4b95ed82c96c380884996ce6460358e7","tid":1627923,"uid":284304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T19:10:12.000Z","msg":"香港有邊D央企"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T19:12:58.000Z","msg":"中銀香港<br />\n中信泰富<br />\n中國人壽<br />\n太平保險<br />\n中國移動<br />\n興業證券"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T19:14:23.000Z","msg":"咪又係呢堆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T19:16:46.000Z","msg":"係架，不過其他民企就放過啦"},{"pid":"a0eeea12c13de607c5b4f88fef712d4383857d0e","tid":1627923,"uid":272292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T19:26:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"07db48dab7d21ce231bf8ce256e181aae99553ae","tid":1627923,"uid":199689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T19:38:12.000Z","msg":"裝修三中商=拆咗中共棵<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">搖錢樹</span></strong><br />\n仲會有免費文宣話俾全世界聽中共已經掌控9成香港出版<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1627873\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1627873</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n三中商由<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">中聯辦</span></strong>全資擁有 唔係藍店紅店而係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">中聯辦分店</span></strong></span> i.e.黑店 <br />\n<br />\n對準政權，三中商咪對準哂囉，西環檔生意呀，控制你睇咩書呀<br />\n中聯辦喺香港搞生意違反基本法呀，夠哂理由未呀<br />\n中聯辦包括三中商，同香港咪敵我矛盾囉<br />\n中聯辦次次干預香港選舉，捐大把政治黑金畀民建聯，仲唔夠資格黑裝修呀？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n或有朋友謂：中聯辦經營書店有什麼問題？<br />\n<br />\n首先，如果中聯辦認為無問題，為何不光明正大，要偷偷摸摸？為何不大大方方承認，站出來解釋他們經營書店的策略與目的，回答記者問題，如何符合一國兩制，如何符合基本法第22條？《鏗鏘集》記者在專輯中多番追問中聯辦各級官員，官員回應不是含糊其辭，就是當作聽不到，閃躲逃避，不肯回答。<br />\n<br />\n中聯辦一直以來協調政黨、協調選舉、組織地區工作，已是公開的秘密，早已違反基本法22(1)「中央人民政府所屬各部門、各省、自治區、直轄市均不得干預香港特別行政區根據本法自行管理的事務。」中聯辦經營書店，或可辯解謂商業運作不屬特區政府管理的事務。不過基本法22(2)則列明，中央各部門要在香港設立機構「須徵得香港特別行政區政府同意並經中央人民政府批准」。《鏗鏘集》查詢政制及內地事務局，特區政府是否知悉？中聯辦此舉有無違反基本法？答覆是「沒有相關資料」。中聯辦經營書店，究竟有無經過合法手續經特區政府同意，還是「國家行為」做什麼都可以？一切疑問，最好就是中聯辦官員面對鏡頭講清楚。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/請認清三中商的幕後老闆/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E8%AB%8B%E8%AA%8D%E6%B8%85%E4%B8%89%E4%B8%AD%E5%95%86%E7%9A%84%E5%B9%95%E5%BE%8C%E8%80%81%E9%97%86%2F&d=AECyLZWdcqpY%2FGgvZN2GpEB1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=415d9aff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E8%AB%8B%E8%AA%8D%E6%B8%85%E4%B8%89%E4%B8%AD%E5%95%86%E7%9A%84%E5%B9%95%E5%BE%8C%E8%80%81%E9%97%86%2F&h=47ba950e\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/請認清三中商的幕後老闆/</a>"}]}